Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rize...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Kaneki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? You've been\Nthrough the wringer, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The master is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did you count?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Five hundred... fifty... nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five hundred... fifty... two...\N--I want to fill this bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five hundred... thirty...\N--Yamori ordered me to count out loud\Nbackward by sevens from one thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--eight...\N--This instruction, which I\Ndidn't understand at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:01:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--is something I now realize was\Nto keep me as sane as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five hundred... thirty... one...\N--is something I now realize was\Nto keep me as sane as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--I was clinging to these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five hundred...\N--I was clinging to these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--twenty... four...\N--Meanwhile, Yamori took my hands and feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,again and again, and again, and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and again, and again, and again,\Nand again, and again, and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and {\i1}AGAIN{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five hundred...\N--and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--ten...\N--Every time my\Nfingers and toes grew back in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five hundred...\N--I knew that I had become a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--three...\N--I knew that I had become a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rize? You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Kaneki, what kind\Nof person was your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "Mom" a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kaneki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're adorable,\Naren't you? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--How do you read this word?\N--You're adorable,\Naren't you? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She would always take\Neach kanji that I couldn't read,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and carefully write down the\Npronunciation next to it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your mother going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's reading room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He died\Nbefore I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know that I came to\Nlove reading because of the books
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that my dad left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you lonesome, all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm. I had my dad's books,\Nand my mom was very nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She really was a terrific person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to work, and did all the housework,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and never once scowled,\Nor caused anyone any trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and treated everyone equally kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom was my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken... it's okay to feel loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice boys like you can\Nbe happy with just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be hurt than to hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice people can be happy with just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She was very nice and wonderful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why you're going through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki, you're a fine one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I'm\Nso particular... toward you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you realize this or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but your regenerative\Npowers are extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to Kanou's experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He made you a ghoul using Rize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One eye. Rize's scent.\NI'm talking about you, Kaneki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the\NChinese red-headed centipede?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to put this in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... Don't... Please...\NI beg you... No...! No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! How fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to kill you! I want to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna kill you!\NWanna kill you! Wanna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I kill\Nyou now? Can I eat you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to kill you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to eat you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me... Kill me... Please, kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be hurt than to hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you really lived your life believing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my mom taught me. So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You obeyed what she\Ntold you to do. What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want him to go to hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure your mother was\Nas nice and wonderful as you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She would always say\Nshe's struggling financially,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask my mom for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Part-time work during the day,\Ngarbage collection by night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and work at home during her\Nfree time. Mom never stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She overworked herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was all alone after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no place to live anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaneki! How long\Nare you gonna stay home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Do you know how hard it is for\Nme when you stay home like this?!\N--Oh, yeah... There was just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...place where I could go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki, if you were a ghoul,\Nwould you eat Yoshikawa in Class 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you like so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I wouldn't!\NAnd I don't like her {\i1}that {\i0}much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide was the only moral support I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a dear friend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're going to lose\Nyour dear friend, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the disadvantage in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,stems from a person's lack of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who told me these\Nwords was a real sack of crap,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but right now, I'm grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki, I've come to understand\Nsomething well these last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,your mind is surprisingly tough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I devised a little plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who love each other...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You will choose which one I kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I let these two look after you until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, you were holding out\Nhope that help was coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw these two as your saviors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't choose, I'll kill them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I rephrase that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you want to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be the one to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up and choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't choose something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like I'm the one\Ndoing the killing, wouldn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick one! Pick one! Pick one! Pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The man? The woman?\NThe right one? The left one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can pick one!\NIf you have to kill someone, kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This one? How about this one?! No?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Pick one! Pick one, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna die! Well, Kaneki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on! Pick one! Pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick me, Mr. Kaneki!\NHaru is... Haru is going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick me! Me! Pick me, Kaneki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She broke, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}all{\i0} your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it's... it's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you just now getting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just sit there blaming yourself,\Nand keep blaming yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but going on blaming\Nyourself won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't try to change. It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That much is obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is it that\Nthings ended up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Coincidence? Accident? Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply a combination of\None circumstance with another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is it that\Ncreates those circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the disadvantage in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,stems from a person's lack of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing started
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're such a fool\Nto the ways of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a fool, and I tricked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor did some tweaking,\Nand we got turned into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be hurt than to hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why you're going through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had been strong and killed Yamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,those two would have been spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had chosen the man,\Nthe woman might have been spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you had been strong at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Ryoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's what's to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you hold most dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you open up to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, you failed to choose. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,this... happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? This is the\Nway of life that you chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the future that you chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying? Why are you sobbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose to be hurt\Nrather than to hurt others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nice and wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But while it seems like you're choosing both,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you're really forsaking both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother was the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If she had turned aside her\Nintolerable sister's requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't have died from overwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a foolish mother, huh? If she loved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she should have abandoned her foolish sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--That's what you really\Nwanted her to do, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stop talking.\N--That's what you really\Nwanted her to do, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...? Why did you leave me all alone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you... I hate being alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish... I wish you would have chosen me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you would have lived... for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant forsaking your aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant hurting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant taking her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kaneki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when you\Nhave to give up on one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to preserve the other.\NYour mother couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't kindness. That's just being weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have the strength--\Nthe resolve to turn her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still remain\Non the side of being hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you abide someone like Yamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If Aogiri gets much stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll soon do a lot of damage\Nto the 20th Ward, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your precious Hide,\Nand your friends at Anteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,might also go through what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who tries to take my\Nplace from me will get no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have that kind of strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you accept me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always surpass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is the wrong choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong... is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That will do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To live is to devour others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... a ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,our special fun time has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The doves are closing in on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my job to take them on, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aogiri's goal is to\Neliminate anyone in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes humans,\Nof course, but ghouls, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghouls who stand\Nopposed to Aogiri's cause--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones where you were\Nworking--"Anteiku," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are also one of Aogiri's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,targets for elimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki! Let me take from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at the end, let me devour all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an inconsequential man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are fantastic, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Devour {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:26.76,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Tell me, oh tell me, the way it works
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:33.77,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Who is that inside of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--? Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:41.07,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Here in this broken-down,\Nbroken-down world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost like the intestines of\Na fish on the verge of spoiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:46.91,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,you laugh, without seeing a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that after everything\Nelse, something like {\i1}that{\i0} hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:07.76,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,I'm just so damaged, I hold my breath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill you... I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat you! I'll make a sloppy mess of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:11.31,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Not even the truth, no not even the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat you! I'll make a sloppy mess of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.77,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,can be unraveled now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll chomp you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:14.73,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:18.23,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Breakable, unbreakable;\Nshakable, unshakable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.94,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,When I found you, it shook me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:28.99,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,In this twisted world, I'm gradually\Ngrowing transparent and vanishing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:36.12,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Don't look for me; don't look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.71,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,I don't wish to hurt you in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:43.13,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,of someone else's imagining
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:47.97,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Remember who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:55.02,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,My full, vivid self
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:04.53,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Entangled in the loneliness\Nthat fans out endlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:08.07,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,stung by the memory\Nof smiling so innocently
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:11.66,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,I can't move, I can't move,\NI can't move, I can't move,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.45,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,I can't move, I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:16.37,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Unraveling the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.77,0:22:47.19,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,I've completely changed;\NI couldn't change back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:50.70,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,The two entwine; the couple penshes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:54.24,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Breakable, unbreakable;\Nshakable, unshakable
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:57.12,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,I won't defile you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:04.96,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,In this shook-up, twisted world, I'm gradually\Ngrowing transparent and vanishing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's one thousand minus seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:12.09,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Don't look for me; don't look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:15.56,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Before the future comes completely undone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:19.18,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,caught in a pit of solitude\Nsomebody set for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's one thousand minus seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:24.02,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,think back on who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is one thousand minus seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:29.90,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,My full, vivid self
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:33.45,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Don't forget me, don't forget me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-Nine hundred... ninety-three...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:36.95,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,don't forget me, don't forget me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nine hundred... eighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:40.46,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,The change over me has me paralyzed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:44.13,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,in an immutable object paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,six...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine hundred... seventy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:48.96,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Remember who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine hundred seventy-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:24:01.89,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,Tell me, tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--Nine hundred sixty... five...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--You tried to devour me.\N--Nine hundred sixty... five...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have no room to complain...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:07.90,Def_I-T,,0,0,0,,is there someone inside of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.94,0:24:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if I eat you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:32.66,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Layout: Katsuya Yamada"
